    FB_MixPumpControl
    - English comments
    - Pressure in mmH2O
    - Uses OSCAT CTRL_PID (v3.33): SUP = DIFF deadband (mmH2O), OFS adds to output Y
    - Includes PV input filter (OSCAT PT1)
    - Includes Jet-to-Wire computation (wire speed in m/min, ratio unitless)
    - Includes ratio tuning via OSCAT TUNE2 (increment/decrement buttons with min/max/step)
    - VFD supervision with RUN feedback timeout
]]></Comment><BitSize>5888</BitSize><SubItem><Name>startCommand</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Start]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>stopCommand</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Stop]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>72</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>autoMode</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE=Auto / FALSE=Manual]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>80</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>pressureFeedback_mmH2O</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Measured pressure [mmH2O]]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>manualOutputPct</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Manual output 0..100%]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>128</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>formingBoardSpeedMPM</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Wire speed [m/min]]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>160</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>jetToWireRatioInc</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Increment ratio button]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>192</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>jetToWireRatioDec</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Decrement ratio button]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>200</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>jetToWi