 METHOD: _RatioInputControl
 Uses OSCAT TUNE2 to adjust jet-to-wire ratio with buttons, step, min/max.
 The instance preserves ratio value across calls (and download if retained).
 ============================================================================]]></Comment></Method><Method><Name>_InputFilter</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ ============================================================================
 METHOD: _InputFilter
 OSCAT PT1 filter for PV, with enable/disable and bumpless behavior.
 When disabled, the filter tracks input quickly (tiny T) to avoid bumps.
 ============================================================================]]></Comment><Parameter><Name>enableFilter</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE=apply PT1, FALSE=bypass]]></Comment><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>rawValue</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Input value to be filtered]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>filterTime</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ PT1 time constant]]></Comment><Type>TIME</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>filterGainK</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ PT1 gain, typically 1.0]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>filteredValue</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Filtered (or bypassed) value]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></Parameter><Local><Name>kUse</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>tUse</Name><Type>TIME</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>yPT1</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local></Method><Method><Name>_JetToWire</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ ============================================================================
 METHOD: _JetToWire
 Computes jet speed from wire speed and ratio, then maps to pressure SP (mmH2O).
 Dynamic head: H[mmH2O] = (v^2 / (2*g)) * 1000, with g = 9.80665 m/s^2.
 A tunable gain/offset is applied; SP is clamped to min/max bounds.
 ============================================================================]]></Comment><Parameter><Name>wireSpeedMPM</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Wire speed [m/min]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>ratio</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Jet/Wire ratio (unitless), e.g., 1.05]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>gainK</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Gain on computed head]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>offset_mmH2O</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Offset added to head [mmH2O]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>minSP_mmH2O</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ SP lower bound [mmH2O]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>maxSP_mmH2O</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ SP upper bound [mmH2O]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>jetSpeed_mps</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Jet speed [m/s]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></Parameter><Parameter><Name>autoSetpoint_mmH2O</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Pressure SP [mmH2O]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></Parameter><Local><Name>wire_mps</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>rUse</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>dynHead_mmH2O</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>cHeadCoeff</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ 1000/(2*g), g=9.80665]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local></Method><Properties><Property><Name>PouType</Name><Value>FunctionBlock</Value></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name Namespace="CPNTeck_OSCAT_BASIC">TP_X</Name><BitSize>320</BitSize><SubItem><Name>IN</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>PT</Name><Type>TIME</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>Q</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>128</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>ET</Name><Type>TIME</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>160</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>edge</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>192</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>start</Name><Type>TIME</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>224</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>tx</Name><Type>TIME</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>256</BitOffs></SubItem><Properties><Property><Name>PouType</Name><Value>FunctionBlock</Value></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name Namespace="CPNTeck_OSCAT_BASIC">PWM_DC</Name><BitSize>768</BitSize><SubItem><Name>F</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>DC</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>Q</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>128</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>clk</Name><Type Namespace="CPNTeck_OSCAT_BASIC">CLK_PRG</Type><BitSize>192</BitSize><BitOffs>192</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>pulse</Name><Type Namespace="CPNTeck_OSCAT_BASIC">TP_X</Type><BitSize>320</BitSize><BitOffs>384</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>tmp</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>704</BitOffs></SubItem><Properties><Property><Name>PouType</Name><Value>FunctionBlock</Value></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name Namespace="CPNTeck_OSCAT_BASIC">CTRL_PWM</Name><BitSize>1024</BitSize><SubItem><Name>CI</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>MAN_IN</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>MANUAL</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>128</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>F</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>160</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>Q</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>192</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>PW</Name><Type Namespace="CPNTeck_OSCAT_BASIC">PWM_DC</Type><BitSize>768</BitSize><BitOffs>256</BitOffs></SubItem><Properties><Property><Name>PouType</Name><Value>FunctionBlock</Value></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name>FB_HeadboxLipsPWMControl</Name><Comment><![CDATA[
    FB_HeadboxLipsPWMControl
    Purpose:
      - Control headbox lips opening using ON/OFF modulation (PWM), no analog speed output.
      - Manual: open/close while buttons are pressed (jog).
      - Automatic: operator types a target opening [mm] and presses "adjust"; the FB drives
        the lips toward the target using PWM duty proportional to position error magnitude.
      - If manualOpenCmd or manualCloseCmd is pressed during automatic positioning, the FB
        immediately returns to manual mode.

    Features:
      - Position units in millimeters (mm).
      - Limit sensors (limitMaxSensor / limitMinSensor) inhibit motion.
      - PWM duty [%] from |positionError| with clamps (min/max duty).
      - Minimum ON time per direction (minOnTime) to protect contactors.
      - Stall detection and travel timeout.
      - Exclusive actuation (never open & close simultaneously).
      - Human-readable deviceState.

    Notes:
      - Single PWM generator; direction is applied by gating its pulse.
      - Target is clamped to [posMin_mm .. posMax_mm].
]]></Comment><BitSize>3648</BitSize><SubItem><Name>positionFeedback_mm</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Actual opening [mm]]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>posMin_mm</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Minimum allowed opening [mm]]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs><Default><Value>0</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>posMax_mm</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Maximum allowed opening [mm]]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>128</BitOffs><Default><Value>25</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>limitMaxSensor</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE when fully open (max) limit is active]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>160</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>limitMinSensor</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE when fully closed (min) limit is active]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>168</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>manualOpenCmd</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Jog open while pressed]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>176</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>manualCloseCmd</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Jog close while pressed]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>184</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>autoTargetInput_mm</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Operator desired opening [mm]]]></Comment><BitSi