omment><BitSize>320</BitSize><BitOffs>6144</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>displayFilterTime</Name><Type>TIME</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Small smoothing (Suavização leve)]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>6464</BitOffs><Default><DateTime>T</DateTime></Default></SubItem><SubItem><Name>jetToWireRatioOld</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>6496</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>manualSetpointOld</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>6528</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>instTON_RunningDelay</Name><Type Namespace="Tc2_Standard">TON</Type><BitSize>256</BitSize><BitOffs>6592</BitOffs></SubItem><SubItem><Name>instTUNE2RatioSetpoint</Name><Type Namespace="CPNTeck_OSCAT_BASIC">TUNE2</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Ratio tuner with min/max clamp]]></Comment><BitSize>640</BitSize><BitOffs>6848</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>TcPersistent</Name></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>instTUNE2ManSetpoint</Name><Type Namespace="CPNTeck_OSCAT_BASIC">TUNE2</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Ratio tuner with min/max clamp]]></Comment><BitSize>640</BitSize><BitOffs>7488</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>TcPersistent</Name></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>jetToWireRatio</Name><Type ReferenceTo="true">REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Current ratio]]></Comment><BitSize>64</BitSize><BitOffs>8128</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>InOut</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>manualSetpoint</Name><Type ReferenceTo="true">REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Manual output 0..100% (Saída manual)	]]></Comment><BitSize>64</BitSize><BitOffs>8192</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>InOut</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><Method><Name>_InputFilter</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ ============================================================================
 METHOD: _InputFilter
 OSCAT PT1 filter for PV, with enable/disable and bumpless behavior.
 When disabled, the filter tracks input quickly (tiny T) to avoid bumps.
 ============================================================================]]></Comment><Parameter><Name>enableFilter</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE=apply PT1, FALSE=bypass]]></Comment><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>rawValue</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Input value to be filtered]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>filterTime</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ PT1 time constant]]></Comment><Type>TIME</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>filterGainK</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ PT1 gain, typically 1.0]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>filteredValue</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Filtered (or bypassed) value]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></Parameter><Local><Name>kUse</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>tUse</Name><Type>TIME</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>yPT1</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local></Method><Method><Name>_JetToWire</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ ============================================================================
 METHOD: _JetToWire
 Computes jet speed from wire speed and ratio, then maps to pressure SP (mmH2O).
 Dynamic head: H[mmH2O] = (v^2 / (2*g)) * 1000, with g = 9.80665 m/s^2.
 A tunable gain/offset is applied; SP is clamped to min/max bounds.
 ============================================================================]]></Comment><Parameter><Name>wireSpeedMPM</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Wire speed [m/min]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>ratio</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Jet/Wire ratio (unitless), e.g., 1.05]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>gainK</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Gain on computed head]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>offset_mmH2O</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Offset added to head [mmH2O]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>minSP_mmH2O</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ SP lower bound [mmH2O]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>maxSP_mmH2O</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ SP upper bound [mmH2O]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Parameter><Parameter><Name>jetSpeed_mps</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Jet speed [m/s]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></Parameter><Parameter><Name>autoSetpoint_mmH2O</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ Pressure SP [mmH2O]]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></Parameter><Local><Name>wire_mps</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>rUse</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>dynHead_mmH2O</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>cHeadCoeff</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ 1000/(2*g), g=9.80665]]></Comment><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local></Method><Method><Name>_FeedbackDisplay</Name><Local><Name>STATUS_IDLE</Name><Type>INT</Type><BitSize>16</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>STATUS_RUNNING</Name><Comment><![CDATA[    STATUS_STARTING : INT := 1;]]></Comment><Type>INT</Type><BitSize>16</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>STATUS_FAULT</Name><Type>INT</Type><BitSize>16</BitSize></Local></Method><Method><Name>_SetpointInputControl</Name><Comment><![CDATA[ ============================================================================
 METHOD: _SetpointInputControl
 Purpose: Handle HMI writes and button nudges for both ratio and manual SP,
          using OSCAT TUNE2 instances. External writes trigger a one-scan
          SET pulse; SU/SD remain active every scan.
 Objetivo: Tratar escritas da HMI e botões ↑/↓ para razão e SP manual,
           usando TUNE2. Escritas externas disparam SET por 1 varredura;
           SU/SD permanecem ativos a cada ciclo.
 ============================================================================]]></Comment></Method><Properties><Property><Name>PouType</Name><Value>FunctionBlock</Value></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name>FB_VfdProcessControler</Name><Comment><![CDATA[
    FB_ProcessControler
    Purpose: Generic process controller with start/stop latch, status codes,
             PID (OSCAT CTRL_PID), optional reverse action, PV PT1 filter,
             engineering↔% scaling, drive run supervision, and HMI displays.

    Sequence: Start pulse toggles RUN latch; Stop pulse/level forces stop.

    Status codes: statusCode INT → 0=Idle, 1=Running, 2=Fault

    Notes: Includes optional low/high PV “hold” with hysteresis (normal-stop class).
]]></Comment><BitSize>8704</BitSize><SubItem><Name>startCommand</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Start pulse toggles RUN latch]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>stopCommand</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Stop pulse/level forces stop]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>72</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointManInc</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Manual output ↑ (0..100%)]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>80</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointManDec</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Manual output ↓ (0..100%)]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>88</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointManSteps</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs><Default><Value>0.1</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointAutoInc</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Auto SP ↑ (engineering units or %)]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>128</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointAutoDec</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Auto SP ↓ (engineering units or %)]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>136</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointAutoSteps</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>160</BitOffs><Default><Value>1</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>autoMode</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE=Automatic / FALSE=Manual]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>192</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>reverseActing</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE: higher output decreases PV; FALSE: direct]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>200</BitOffs><Default><Bool>false</Bool></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processFeedbackEng</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ PV (engineering units), e.g., bar/kPa/°C/…]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>224</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>kp</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Proportional gain (sign handled via reverseActing)]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>256</BitOffs><Default><Value>1</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>tn</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Integral time [s]]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>288</BitOffs><Default><Value>8</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>tv</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Derivative time [s]]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>320</BitOffs><Default><Value>0</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>outLowLimitPct</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Min output %]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>352</BitOffs><Default><Value>0</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>outHig