 METHOD: _SetpointInputControl
 Purpose: Handle HMI writes for manual output using OSCAT TUNE2. Any external
          write to manualOutputPct bigger than the configured step will pulse
          SET for one scan. No SU/SD buttons here (PressureCtrl doesn’t use them).
 Objetivo: Tratar escrita da HMI no manualOutputPct via TUNE2. Mudança externa
           > passo gera pulso SET de 1 varredura. Sem botões ↑/↓ neste FB.
 ============================================================================]]></Comment><Local><Name>spManClamped</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local><Local><Name>spAutoClamped</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize></Local></Method><Properties><Property><Name>PouType</Name><Value>FunctionBlock</Value></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name>FB_WirePitControl</Name><Comment><![CDATA[
    FB_ProcessControler
    Purpose: Generic process controller with start/stop latch, status codes,
             PID (OSCAT CTRL_PID), optional reverse action, PV PT1 filter,
             engineering↔% scaling, drive run supervision, and HMI displays.

    Sequence: Start pulse toggles RUN latch; Stop pulse/level forces stop.

    Status codes: statusCode INT → 0=Idle, 1=Running, 2=Fault

    Notes: Includes optional low/high PV “hold” with hysteresis (normal-stop class).
