    FB_ProcessControler
    Purpose: Generic process controller with start/stop latch, status codes,
             PID (OSCAT CTRL_PID), optional reverse action, PV PT1 filter,
             engineering↔% scaling, drive run supervision, and HMI displays.

    Sequence: Start pulse toggles RUN latch; Stop pulse/level forces stop.

    Status codes: statusCode INT → 0=Idle, 1=Running, 2=Fault

    Notes: Includes optional low/high PV “hold” with hysteresis (normal-stop class).
]]></Comment><BitSize>9088</BitSize><SubItem><Name>startCommand</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Start pulse toggles RUN latch]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>stopCommand</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Stop pulse/level forces stop]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>72</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointManInc</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Manual output ↑ (0..100%)]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>80</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointManDec</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Manual output ↓ (0..100%)]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>88</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointManSteps</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs><Default><Value>0.1</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointAutoInc</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Auto SP ↑ (engineering units or %)]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>128</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointAutoDec</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Auto SP ↓ (engineering units or %)]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>136</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>processSetpointAutoSteps</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>160</BitOffs><Default><Value>1</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><V